OL,4,Cwalker after losing control of vehicle
OL,6,FA driver killed a dog walker after
OL,7,Fflipping his car while "showing off"
OL,8,Fand losing control of his vehicle.
OL,10,FDaniel Boucher, 28, struck and killed
OL,11,F66-year-old David Chaplin after he
OL,12,Flost control of his red Peugeot 207
OL,13,Fwhich left the road as he failed to
OL,14,Fnegotiate a left bend. The car rolled
OL,15,Fonto its side and struck Mr Chaplin
OL,16,Fwho was later found unconscious on a
OL,17,Fgrass verge.
OL,19,FChaplin suffered multiple traumatic
OL,20,Finjuries and died at the roadside.
