OL,6,FBoucher was found guilty on 16 May of
OL,7,Fcausing death by dangerous driving,
OL,8,Ffollowing a trial at Cardiff Crown
OL,9,FCourt.
OL,11,FHe had denied this charge and had
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to the lesser offence
OL,13,Fof causing death by careless/
OL,14,Finconsiderate driving but this plea
OL,15,Fwas rejected by the jury.
