OL,3,CDriver found guilty for killing dog
OL,4,Cwalker after losing control of vehicle
OL,6,FOpening the case to the jury,
OL,7,Fprosecutor Owen Williams said the
OL,8,Fdefendant worked for a window cleaning
OL,9,Ffirm based in Caerphilly and was
OL,10,Fleaving premises at Whitebeam
OL,11,Findustrial estate at around 5.10pm on
OL,12,F18 April, 2023 when the collision
OL,13,Foccurred.
OL,15,FThe defendant had been speaking to
OL,16,Fcolleague Scott Williams about his
OL,17,Flove for cars. He had told Williams
OL,18,Fhis Peugeot was "turbo-charged" and
OL,19,Fhad brake horsepower between 165 and
OL,20,F170.
