OL,4,Cwalker after losing control of vehicle
OL,6,FParamedics and police later arrived
OL,7,Fand took over Mr Chaplin's treatment
OL,8,Fbut despite their best efforts he was
OL,9,Fpronounced dead at the scene. A cause
OL,10,Fof death was later given as multiple
OL,11,Ftraumatic injuries.
OL,13,FPolice officers arrested Boucher. He
OL,14,Ftold them "I lost control of the car"
OL,15,Fand confirmed he was driving over the
OL,16,Fspeed limit.
OL,18,FHe did not respond to his arrest and
OL,19,Fcautioned but he later said: "What
OL,20,Fhave I done, I'm sorry."
