OL,6,FFollowing the guilty verdicts, Judge
OL,7,FVanessa Francis thanked the jury for
OL,8,Ftheir service.
OL,10,FThe judge told Boucher he would be
OL,11,Freceiving a custodial sentence but
OL,12,Fremanded the defendant on bail while a
OL,13,Fpre-sentence report is prepared and to
OL,14,Fallow for him to put his affairs in
OL,15,Forder.
OL,17,FThe defendant will appear at the
OL,18,FCardiff Crown Court on 23 June for
OL,19,Fsentencing.
